---

## Phase 1: Immediate Response (First 5 minutes)

### Acknowledge

- [ ] Incident acknowledged
- [ ] War room created
- [ ] On-call engineer paged
- [ ] Stakeholders notified (if SEV1)

### Initial Assessment

- [ ] **Impact identified**: Who/what is affected?
- [ ] **Scope determined**: How many users/services?
- [ ] **Severity confirmed**: SEV1 / SEV2 / SEV3 / SEV4
- [ ] **Start time recorded**: {{incident.startedAt}}

### Communication Setup

- [ ] Incident bridge/room created
- [ ] Relevant engineers invited
- [ ] Incident Slack channel: `#incident-{{incident.id}}`
- [ ] Status page updated

---

## Phase 2: Investigation (5-30 minutes)

### Data Collection

- [ ] Metrics checked ( dashboards)
- [ ] Logs reviewed
- [ ] Alerts examined
- [ ] Recent deployments identified
- [ ] External dependencies checked

### Hypothesis Formation

- [ ] Root cause hypothesis: _______________
- [ ] Evidence supporting hypothesis: _______________
- [ ] Alternative hypotheses: _______________

### Mitigation Attempt

- [ ] Quick mitigation identified: _______________
- [ ] Mitigation applied: YES / NO
- [ ] Result: _______________

---

## Phase 3: Resolution (30+ minutes)

### Fix Implementation

- [ ] Fix identified
- [ ] Fix tested in staging
- [ ] Rollback prepared
- [ ] Fix deployed
- [ ] Fix verified

### Monitoring

- [ ] Metrics returning to normal
- [ ] Error rates decreasing
- [ ] Latency improving
- [ ] No new alerts firing

---

## Phase 4: Communication

### Internal Updates

| Time | Status | Notes |
|------|--------|-------|
| T+15m | Investigating | [Initial findings] |
| T+30m | Identified | [Root cause] |
| T+60m | Mitigating | [Fix applied] |
| T+90m | Monitoring | [Verifying fix] |

### External Updates

- [ ] Status page updated
- [ ] Customer notification sent (if required)
- [ ] Leadership briefed

---

## Phase 5: Resolution

### Confirmation

- [ ] All services healthy
- [ ] No residual issues
- [ ] Metrics stable for 15 minutes

### Incident Closed

- [ ] Incident closed in PagerDuty
- [ ] Status page updated to resolved
- [ ] All stakeholders notified
- [ ] Post-mortem scheduled

